name: Virtue of courage
description:
Continuing the cycle of life, a role marks us among the challenges proposed by the inhospitable environment such as in the northeastern hinterland of Brazil. Be a coward or use the virtue of courage. Floating in this trance of madness worthy of the hero's journey. Enjoy the background sound produced by the great soul reader, @fantonbeat, to immerse yourself in its ascension.

audiotrack: @fantonbeat
